  "description": "Consolidates every scattered auth path (tokens.json, SOS_SYSTEM_TOKEN env, MIRROR_TOKEN env, BUS_BRIDGE_TOKEN, CYRUS_BUS_TOKEN, etc.) behind a single sos.services.auth module exposing verify_bearer(auth_header) -> AuthContext. Callers stop reading env vars and tokens.json directly. Adds integration tests for scope matrix (system/admin/tenant/agent).",
